Package: oligoGames
Type: Package
Title: Analyze data from massively parallel reporter assays
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Chinmay Shukla <cshukla@fas.harvard.edu>, Keegan Korthauer
    <keegan@jimmy.harvard.edu>, Rafael Irizarry <rafa@jimmy.harvard.edu>
Maintainer: Chinmay Shukla <cshukla@fas.harvard.edu>
Description: Analyzing data from massively parallel reporter assays. Allows user
    to design an oligo pool and generate oligo sequences, map fastq files to the
    barcodes, model oligo count data to obtain nucleotide resolution count data and
    finally make inferences about peak regions from the modelled data.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.3.2)
Imports:
    EBSeq,
    utils,
    dplyr,
    reshape2,
    tidyr,
    GenomicRanges,
    bumphunter,
    bsseq,
    splines,
    doParallel
License: GPL (>=2)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
